- Prepare the server (see vps setup)
- Add a privatekey to the new server in your old host
- copy over the files using rsync (perhaps the apps directory)
- update bundles
- copy over nginx configuration
- Copy over postgres databases and start server
- bundle exec unicorn -E production -c config/unicorn.rb
- Daemonize above if satisfied
- Install elasticsearch
- Update elasticsearch cache
- Install backup gem and copy over backup folder
- Update cron tasks
- Update DNS